Package game.Items.token

Class TokenOfSouls

java.lang.Object
edu.monash.fit2099.engine.Item
game.Items.token.TokenOfSouls
All Implemented Interfaces:
DesignOSoulsAddOn, Capable, Printable, Soul
public class TokenOfSouls extends Item implements Soul
A class that represent the Token of Soul. Managed by Token Manager. The program can hold at most 2 Token at a time, where one should be removed before placing another one. It can only be created, drop and picked up by the player.
Version:
1
Author:
Shin Yung Xin
